reviewText: My favorite video as a kid. I watched it multiple times a day. The video is hosted by J. Cricket and features Mickey, Donald, Goofy and Pluto on their own hillarious vacations.  Donald on a Dude Ranch, Goofy fishing, Mickey golfing with his pal Pluto. It is all priceless.

I grew up on this tape!  If you want the best of Mickey & Pals, look no further!  The downside- it's VHS.  The copy my parents had was beta.  So until this gets redone to fit modern times, put this on your wishlist!!!

This 1956 TV Special, originally released on VHS in 1982 is hosted by Jiminy Cricket. In this VHS exclusive, Jiminy Cricket introduces the classic cartoon shorts Canine Caddy (starring Mickey and Pluto), Bubble Bee (starring Pluto), Goofy and Wilbur (starring Goofy and Wilbur), Dude Duck (starring Donald Duck), Mickey's Trailer (starring Mickey Mouse, Donald Duck and Goofy) and Hawaiian Holiday (starring Mickey Mouse, Minnie Mouse, Donald Duck, Goofy and Pluto).
